      },
      "type": "term",
      "surface": {
        "jp": "論理積",
        "zh": "逻辑与",
        "en": "Logical AND"
      },
      "definition": {
        "jp": "二つの真偽値入力がどちらも真（1）のときに真（1）を、それ以外のときに偽（0）を出力する論理演算（AND演算の日本語名称）。",
        "zh": "两个布尔输入都为真（1）时输出真（1），否则输出假（0）的逻辑运算。日语称为「論理積」。",
        "en": "A logical operation that outputs true (1) only when both Boolean inputs are true (1), and outputs false (0) otherwise. (Japanese name: 論理積)"
      },
      "kana_helper": null
    },
    {
      "id": "itpassport_r6::term::p327::1",
      "anchor": {
        "page": 327,
        "block_id": "page_327_block_1",
        "section_path": []
      },
      "type": "term",
      "surface": {
        "jp": "論理和",
        "zh": "逻辑或",
        "en": "Logical OR"
      },
      "definition": {
        "jp": "二つの真偽値入力の少なくとも一方が真（1）のときに真（1）を、両方とも偽のときだけ偽（0）を出力する論理演算（OR演算の日本語名称）。",
        "zh": "两个布尔输入中至少有一个为真（1）时输出真（1），仅当两者都为假时输出假（0）的逻辑运算。日语称为「論理和」。",
        "en": "A logical operation that outputs true (1) whenever at least one Boolean input is true (1), and outputs false (0) only when both inputs are false. (Japanese name: 論理和)"
      },
      "kana_helper": null
    },
    {
      "id": "itpassport_r6::term::p327::2",
      "anchor": {
        "page": 327,
        "block_id": "page_327_block_2",
        "section_path": []
      },
      "type": "term",
      "surface": {
        "jp": "排他的論理和",
        "zh": "异或",
        "en": "Exclusive OR (XOR)"
      },
      "definition": {
        "jp": "二つの真偽値入力が異なる（一方が真で一方が偽）ときに真（1）を、同じ値のときに偽（0）を出力する論理演算（XOR演算の日本語名称）。",
        "zh": "两个布尔输入不同（一真一假）时输出真（1），相同时输出假（0）的逻辑运算（XOR）。日语称为「排他的論理和」。",
        "en": "A logical operation that outputs true (1) when the two Boolean inputs differ (one true, one false), and outputs false (0) when they match. (Japanese name: 排他的論理和)"
      },
      "kana_helper": null
    },
    {
      "id": "itpassport_r6::term::p327::3",
      "anchor": {
        "page": 327,
        "block_id": "page_327_block_3",
        "section_path": []
      },
      "type": "term",
      "surface": {
        "jp": "否定",
        "zh": "否定",
        "en": "Negation"
      },
      "definition": {
        "jp": "単一の真偽値入力を反転させる単項論理演算（0→1、1→0）。NOT演算の日本語名称。",
        "zh": "将单个布尔输入反转的一元运算（0→1，1→0）。日语称为「否定」。",
        "en": "A unary logical operation that inverts a single Boolean input (0→1, 1→0). (Japanese name: 否定)"
      },
      "kana_helper": null
    },
    {
      "id": "itpassport_r6::term::p327::4",
      "anchor": {
        "page": 327,
        "block_id": "page_327_block_4",
        "section_path": []
      },
      "type": "term",
      "surface": {
        "jp": "NAND",
        "zh": "逻辑与非（NAND）",
        "en": "NAND"
      },
      "definition": {
        "jp": "否定論理積。論理積と否定を組み合わせた演算で、AND演算の答えをすべて反転する(0は1、1は0)。「NOT AND」の意味。",
        "zh": "与非（NAND）。将逻辑与与否定相结合的运算，将AND运算的结果全部反转（0变为1，1变为0）。即「NOT AND」之意。",
        "en": "NAND (Negative AND). An operation combining logical AND with negation, inverting all results of the AND operation (0 becomes 1, 1 becomes 0). It means \"NOT AND\"."
      },
      "kana_helper": null
    },
    {
      "id": "itpassport_r6::term::p327::5",
      "anchor": {
        "page": 327,
        "block_id": "page_327_block_5",
        "section_path": []
      },
      "type": "term",
      "surface": {
        "jp": "NOR",
        "zh": "逻辑或非（NOR）",
        "en": "NOR"
      },
      "definition": {
        "jp": "否定論理和。論理和と否定を組み合わせた演算で、OR演算の答えをすべて反転させる。「NOT OR」の意味。",
        "zh": "或非（NOR）。将逻辑或与否定相结合的运算，将OR运算的结果全部反转。即「NOT OR」之意。",
        "en": "NOR (Negative OR). An operation combining logical OR with negation, inverting all results of the OR operation. It means \"NOT OR\"."
      },
      "kana_helper": null
    },
